Texts.Chs: 我可以打开飞船的短距离传送，它会带你到下面的星球。请谨慎探索！
Texts.Eng: I can turn on the ship's short range teleport, it'll take you down to the planet below. Be careful down there!

Texts.Chs: 我成功了！现在我们可以进入这个星球，我们可以找到那些我们需要的材料来修理飞船的推进器！
Texts.Eng: I did it! Now we have access to the planet we can find those materials we need to fix the ship's thrusters!
